From 3fc9621d9811d3c0173c20d96410be1b837470a3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:36:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] graphic_2d: adapt render service and EGL stack for
 hybris_generic container

Multiple fixes to make the OHOS Rosen render pipeline work with Android HALs
via libhybris inside an LXC container:

boot_compatible_display_strategy.cpp: Poll GetDefaultScreenId() until a valid
screen ID is available. The HIDL hotplug callback is async, so there is a
window between bootevent.renderservice.ready=true and the default screen ID
being set. Without the retry loop, boot animation fails immediately.

egl_wrapper_display.cpp: Remove the strict EGLDisplay pointer equality check
in GetWrapperDisplay(). On hybris the impl may return a different handle from
the singleton wrapper address; since there is only one physical display, map
any non-null handle to the singleton.

render_context_gl.cpp: Use eglGetDisplay() (linked wrapper symbol) instead of
eglGetProcAddress("eglGetPlatformDisplayEXT"). The latter returns the impl's raw
function pointer, bypassing the OHOS EGL wrapper and producing a display handle
that fails all subsequent wrapper validation. Hardcode the GLES version string
to "OpenGL ES 3.2" to avoid a SIGSEGV from glGetString() with no GL context.
Remove the spurious eglMakeCurrent(NO_SURFACE) call before eglCreateWindowSurface.

vsync_distributor.cpp: Raise MAX_PID from 65536 to 4194304 (Linux PID_MAX_LIMIT).
LXC containers share the host PID namespace; high-numbered host PIDs were silently
dropped by the VSyncConnection connection table, causing missed vsync callbacks.

rs_base_render_engine.cpp: Guard Init() against EGL context creation failure so
render_service does not abort when the GPU is temporarily unavailable.

rs_screen_manager.cpp: Add fallback in ProcessScreenConnected() to claim a screen
as default when defaultScreenId_ is still INVALID after the MIPI check. Fixes an
async hotplug race where the MIPI check flag was already set on an empty queue.

rs_ipc_interface_code_access_verifier_base.cpp: Return TOKEN_NATIVE for token IDs
below 10000 (raw UIDs from Android binder). Real OHOS tokens have type bits at
bit 27-28 and are always >= 0x08000000.

rs_surface_ohos_gl.cpp: Add debug log before RenderFrame/SwapBuffers to trace
EGL surface lifetime issues (Phase 8.17 eglSwapBuffers/eglDestroySurface race).

Covers Phase 6.11-6.12 (boot animation, first frame), Phase 6.10D (IPC token
fallback), and Phase 8 stability fixes for hybris_generic.

Change-Id: I5a70ed987ec6c3628492b4101b9b69bdb7ea6047
